 "remarks": "This is the one you&apos;ve been waiting for. Perfectly blending timeless architecture with exceptional in-town convenience, this stunning five-bedroom Colonial, designed by renowned local architect Neil Hauck, is nestled on one of the area&apos;s most coveted streets.  The thoughtfully designed floor plan is ideal for both everyday living and entertaining. At the heart of the home is a spectacular gourmet kitchen that flows seamlessly into the inviting family room, complete with a fireplace and dramatic oversized windows that flood the space with natural light.  Step outside to your own private retreat, where a beautifully manicured lawn, mature landscaping, and a spacious stone patio create the perfect setting for outdoor dining, entertaining, or simply relaxing.  The first floor offers a private guest bedroom, while the second level features four additional bedrooms, including a serene primary suite. A finished third floor provides the perfect flex space for a playroom, home office, media room, or workout area.  Combining exceptional craftsmanship, an unbeatable location, and effortless in-town living, this is a rare opportunity to own a truly special home. Don&apos;t miss it!",
